ActInternational Boundary Waters Treaty Act
PrecisEnactment of the INTERNATIONAL BOUNDARY WATERS REGULATIONS which specify the information that must be contained in an application for a licence to remove or use boundary waters in bulk, or for the renewal or amendment thereof, and that a licence must include the conditions applicable thereto.
